						<p><img src="../images/sub06/bullet_red_02.gif" width="8" height="9" alt="" />Develop technologies for enhanced oil recovery using CO2</p>
						<p><img src="../images/sub06/bullet_red_02.gif" width="8" height="9" alt="" />Make reports on low carbon, green growth technology trends</p>
